{"title":"PCR Avanzado UCI iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/PCR Avanzado UCI iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Paro Cardiorrespiratorio\\NAvanzado en UCI","guid":"2wdzgqSHXIHyvl5VBnimMA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"IHCA incidencia ~1.6-6.5% admisiones UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Supervivencia al alta hospitalaria ~23.6% adultos (AHA 2025)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"OHCA supervivencia al alta ~10.5% (AHA 2025)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"AM >70a → supervivencia al alta IHCA 11.6-28.5%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"AM >70a → supervivencia al alta OHCA 0-11.1%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Frágiles (CFS ≥5) → mortalidad 1 año 64.8% vs 36.4% no frágiles","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"Cada punto CFS → HR 1.22 (IC 95% 1.19-1.26) mortalidad 1 año","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Reconocimiento\\Nen UCI","guid":"p2AEzvwqAyt9QcOuHGEWaw","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Monitorización continua → detección precoz","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"RITMOS\\NDESFIBRILABLES","guid":"lo1YsPY-IqPXatzn-zBtmg","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"FV (fibrilación ventricular)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"TV sin pulso (taquicardia ventricular)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"RITMOS NO\\NDESFIBRILABLES","guid":"8H-aM0QyKG6mDKvvN6pgFQ","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Asistolía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"AESP (actividad eléctrica sin pulso)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"9","text":"Verificar → ausencia pulso + apnea/gasping","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"9","text":"En UCI → capnografía waveform confirma PCR (ETCO2 <10 mmHg)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"0","text":"Algoritmo ACLS\\N(AHA 2025)","guid":"RMC_uNqnim4MqTPMWbS4Aw","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Inicio INMEDIATO de RCP\\Nde alta calidad","guid":"ODn388hH1IGTEFxKeaqE5A","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Compresiones 100-120/min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Profundidad 5-6 cm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"Descompresión completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"Minimizar interrupciones (<10 seg)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"Relación 30:2 sin vía aérea avanzada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"Compresiones continuas con vía aérea avanzada → 1 ventilación cada 6 seg","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"19","text":"VÍA AÉREA\\NAVANZADA","guid":"FTVF_nbd7gIqWCfg9Uhd5w","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Intubación orotraqueal → gold standard en UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Videolaringoscopía si disponible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Capnografía waveform → confirmar posición + monitorizar calidad RCP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"ETCO2 >20 mmHg → compresiones adecuadas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"27","text":"Aumento súbito ETCO2 → posible ROSC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"19","text":"RITMO DESFIBRILABLE\\N(FV/TV sin pulso)","guid":"lOi7Uh7MRCrV_8xo_tnA6g","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Desfibrilación PRECOZ → prioridad absoluta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Bifásica 120-200 J (según fabricante)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Monofásica 360 J","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"RCP 2 min entre descargas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"EPINEFRINA 1 mg IV/IO → tras 2do shock","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Repetir cada 3-5 min","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"33","text":"AMIODARONA\\N→ tras 3er shock","guid":"42BfZ-VB1-Zo5e8c-K-WPg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Primera dosis 300 mg IV/IO en bolo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Segunda dosis 150 mg IV/IO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"33","text":"LIDOCAÍNA\\Nalternativa a\\Namiodarona","guid":"0OBZKR_9LkK8s_1mE-d6KA","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Primera dosis 1-1.5 mg/kg IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Segunda dosis 0.5-0.75 mg/kg IV","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"33","text":"FV REFRACTARIA\\N(AHA 2025)","guid":"FntSjE6yFdc4vA19ZhSqWA","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Considerar doble desfibrilación secuencial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Cambiar posición parches (anteroposterior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"ECPR si disponible y causa reversible","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"19","text":"RITMO NO DESFIBRILABLE\\N(asistolía/AESP)","guid":"cLd_8w4D58TPPqcfSlBF-Q","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"RCP inmediata continua","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"EPINEFRINA 1 mg IV/IO → lo antes posible","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Repetir cada 3-5 min","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Amiodarona NO indicada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"Buscar CAUSAS REVERSIBLES → prioridad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"Ecografía point-of-care → identificar causa","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Causas Reversibles\\N→ H y T","guid":"5xq1WrZc6vDejWLgrCs6mw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"5 H","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Hipovolemia → fluidos IV, sangre si hemorragia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Hipoxia → vía aérea avanzada, FiO2 100%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Hidrogeniones (acidosis) → tratar causa, NaHCO3 selectivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"Hipo/Hiperkalemia → Ca gluconato, insulina+dextrosa, NaHCO3","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"Hipotermia → recalentamiento activo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"57","text":"5 T","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Neumotórax a Tensión → descompresión con aguja → tubo pleural","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Taponamiento cardíaco → pericardiocentesis guiada por eco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Tóxicos → antídotos específicos (naloxona, flumazenil, lípidos IV)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"Trombosis pulmonar → trombolíticos sistémicos, considerar ECMO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"Trombosis coronaria → ICP si sospecha SCA","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"57","text":"EN UCI → causas\\Nmás frecuentes","guid":"hotTRVUCt8qz9Zz5W6pgZQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Hipoxemia por desconexión/obstrucción TET","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"Hiperkalemia → IRC, fármacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"Neumotórax → post procedimiento (CVC, VM)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"Taponamiento → post cirugía cardíaca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"70","text":"TEP masivo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"0","text":"Acceso\\NVascular y\\NFármacos","guid":"u_vP5kEbKVMFsd5DIO7YXA","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"VÍA IV → primera opción en UCI (ya disponible)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"CVC preferible → administración rápida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"VÍA INTRAÓSEA → si no hay acceso IV","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Tibia proximal o húmero","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"76","text":"EPINEFRINA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"1 mg cada 3-5 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"NO usar dosis altas → sin beneficio (AHA 2025)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"76","text":"VASOPRESINA → no recomendada como reemplazo de epinefrina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"76","text":"AMIODARONA\\Nvs LIDOCAÍNA","guid":"5VL9Vsj5ig9TlJs-apwNSA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Amiodarona primera línea FV/TV refractaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"Lidocaína alternativa aceptable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"Sin diferencia significativa en supervivencia al alta","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"76","text":"Bicarbonato\\Nde sodio","guid":"TRl_XLjzNjmM1TfwQz7bfg","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"NO rutinario en PCR indiferenciado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"SÍ en hiperkalemia o intoxicación por tricíclicos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"76","text":"Calcio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"NO rutinario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"SÍ en hiperkalemia, hipocalcemia, bloqueadores de calcio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"76","text":"Magnesio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Solo en Torsades de Pointes → 1-2 g IV","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"ECPR (RCP\\Ncon ECMO)","guid":"rmBCiSWJP_fIylni7KsaMA","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Indicaciones\\Npotenciales","guid":"olzVX0OYXGEaaNifbY0n7w","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"PCR refractario a medidas convencionales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"Causa potencialmente reversible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"RCP de buena calidad <60 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"98","text":"Paciente sin contraindicación para anticoagulación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"97","text":"Evidencia\\N(AHA\\N2023/2025)","guid":"sP8PKEZtvzDAUy8pKJmMUw","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"2 RCTs publicados post-2020","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Beneficio potencial en centros con experiencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"NO recomendado de rutina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"103","text":"Requiere programa establecido y entrenado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"97","text":"Contraindicaciones\\Nrelativas en AM","guid":"oG9gi5HQiNI5TTQF74J4Sw","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Fragilidad severa (CFS ≥7)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Comorbilidad avanzada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"Directrices anticipadas limitantes","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Cuidados Post-Paro\\N(AHA 2025)","guid":"KkBE2vbovFasRLqPrZ29Kg","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"MANEJO\\NHEMODINÁMICO","guid":"V_VT1CfOleeVKElcJcf-3Q","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"PAM ≥65 mmHg (individualizar)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Sin evidencia para metas PAM elevadas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"Vasopresores → norepinefrina primera línea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"Ecocardiografía precoz → evaluar función ventricular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"113","text":"Coronariografía si sospecha SCA → individualizar timing","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"112","text":"CONTROL DE\\NTEMPERATURA\\N(TTM)","guid":"duGf1xN_3JSR1ucIkPNXhA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"AHA 2023 → temperatura <37.5°C por ≥24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Prevenir activamente fiebre >37.5°C","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"Objetivo individualizado (33-36°C ya no obligatorio)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"Mantener normotermia activa ≥72h post-ROSC","guid":"Sv2pd6KibRSHoOeIgiHCCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"112","text":"VENTILACIÓN Y\\NOXIGENACIÓN","guid":"EIxVtKSIRwihvZZRwWlDDQ","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"FiO2 100% inicial → titular a SpO2 92-98%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"EVITAR hipoxemia → fuerte recomendación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"124","text":"EVITAR hiperoxia → daño oxidativo potencial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"Normocapnia → PaCO2 35-45 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"124","text":"Ventilación protectora → Vt 6-8 mL/kg peso ideal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"112","text":"NEUROPROGNÓSTICACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"NO antes de 72h post-ROSC en normotérmicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"Multimodal OBLIGATORIO → no usar un solo predictor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"Herramientas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Examen neurológico → reflejo pupilar, corneal, motor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"EEG → reactividad, patrones ictales-interictales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"Potenciales evocados somatosensoriales (N20)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"Neuroimagen (TC/RM cerebral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"Biomarcadores → NSE (enolasa neurona-específica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"130","text":"Anticonvulsivantes no sedantes → si patrones ictales-interictales (AHA 2023)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"112","text":"MANEJO DE\\NCONVULSIONES","guid":"PlhCzbJbF5Jt5rwrAi43gQ","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"EEG continuo si comatoso post-ROSC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Tratar convulsiones clínicas y electroencefalográficas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"Levetiracetam → primera línea (no sedante)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"Ácido valproico → alternativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"EVITAR profilaxis anticonvulsivante rutinaria","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"146","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas en UCI","guid":"AdUs0QpyhP9CLngJYuBDuQ","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"ANTES DEL PCR\\N→ PREVENCIÓN","guid":"sBxyac0G11R64Y_NI0xrKA","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"Definir CÓDIGO DE STATUS al ingreso UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"Conversación con paciente/familia sobre DIRECTRICES ANTICIPADAS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"Evaluar CFS pre-mórbido → predictor independiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"147","text":"CFS ≥5 → discutir proporcionalidad de RCP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"147","text":"Revisar polifarmacia → fármacos proarrítmicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"147","text":"QTc prolongado → antipsicóticos, macrólidos, fluoroquinolonas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"147","text":"Electrolitos → K+, Mg2+, Ca2+ monitoreo estrecho","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"146","text":"DURANTE\\NEL PCR","guid":"YSdjbb7hnK58Qrp6QkxMHA","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"Mismo algoritmo ACLS → la edad NO es contraindicación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Fragilidad torácica → riesgo fractura costal/esternal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"Calcificación valvular → menor respuesta a compresiones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"155","text":"Menor reserva fisiológica → ROSC más difícil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"155","text":"Ajustar expectativas → duración razonable de esfuerzo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"146","text":"POST-ROSC\\NEN AM","guid":"GfL6Q3yEE_BnOFJOWWagUA","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"Mayor riesgo de daño neurológico post-anóxico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"Delirium post-PCR → CAM-ICU sistemático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"161","text":"Disfagia post-intubación → screening antes de alimentación oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"Movilización precoz → prevenir síndrome post-UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"161","text":"Deprescripción activa → revisar todos los fármacos al reinicio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"161","text":"Nutrición → proteínas 1.2-1.5 g/kg/día, valorar MNA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"161","text":"Rehabilitación temprana → Kinesioterapia desde día 1","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"146","text":"DECISIONES\\NÉTICAS","guid":"4MPHY0QO8Y5g1rEYPJzTcg","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Proporcionalidad terapéutica → evaluar caso a caso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"EDAD NO es criterio único para limitar esfuerzo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"Fragilidad + comorbilidad + preferencias = decisión integral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"Reunión familiar estructurada → información clara y honesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"169","text":"Considerar CUIDADOS PALIATIVOS si pronóstico ominoso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"169","text":"Donación de órganos → considerar si aplica (AHA 2023)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Calidad de\\NRCP en UCI","guid":"V8XeVeTOHT0njJ_Imb03Vg","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Monitorización\\Nen tiempo real","guid":"SOSJQv7y-AEOPinbasaQ9g","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"Capnografía waveform → ETCO2 >20 mmHg como meta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"Presión arterial invasiva → presión diastólica >25 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"Feedback audiovisual de compresiones si disponible","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"176","text":"Debriefing post-evento\\N→ OBLIGATORIO","guid":"_JG_RnMcaJGNJkPtenOb-g","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"Análisis del evento dentro de 24-48h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"Identificar brechas en reconocimiento y respuesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"Apoyo emocional al equipo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"176","text":"Factores que mejoran\\Noutcomes en UCI","guid":"LH8zBdEzV85BlwrURE04wg","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Detección precoz → alarmas, monitoreo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"Equipo entrenado in situ","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"Desfibrilación <3 min desde reconocimiento","guid":"U0OoditFDIH7fvBKZrnC3w","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"Acceso vascular ya establecido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"185","text":"Capnografía disponible","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"gdWKTTlOP-1XX-SlAgGBUA","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"ETCO2 <10 mmHg sostenido tras 20 min RCP → considerar cese (pronóstico ominoso)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"Aumento súbito de ETCO2 durante RCP → posible ROSC, verificar pulso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"191","text":"Presión diastólica invasiva <20 mmHg → mejorar calidad compresiones antes de fármacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"191","text":"En UCI el PCR es frecuentemente NO desfibrilable → buscar H y T inmediatamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"191","text":"Hiperkalemia es la causa reversible MÁS TRATABLE → Ca gluconato + insulina/dextrosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"191","text":"CFS pre-mórbido ≥5 → HR 1.22 por punto para mortalidad 1 año post-PCR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"191","text":"NaHCO3 NO mejora outcomes en PCR indiferenciado → puede empeorar supervivencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"191","text":"La edad sola NO predice outcome → fragilidad y estado funcional son mejores predictores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"191","text":"Post-ROSC → EVITAR hiperoxia y mantener normocapnia (PaCO2 35-45)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"191","text":"Neuropropósticación multimodal → NUNCA antes de 72h, NUNCA con un solo test","guid":"NBlZTVd54QcuYydMoFJVSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIÉN","guid":"r6MKjQro3YUBro-uHcpMDQ","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Síndromes Geriátricos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"→ Fragilidad y CFS (Valoración Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"→ Sedación y Analgesia UCI (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"→ Proporcionalidad Terapéutica (Bioética)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"→ Polifarmacia y Deprescripción (Farmacología Geriátrica)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"→ Ventilación Mecánica (Cuidados Críticos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"→ Arritmias (Cardiogeriatría)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"202","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Síndromes Geriátricos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"202","text":"→ Fragilidad y CFS (Valoración Geriátrica)","guid":"Wu24b_agI1FiICHDRHc89g","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"202","text":"→ Sedación UCI (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"202","text":"→ Proporcionalidad Terapéutica (Bioética)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"202","text":"→ Arritmias (Cardiogeriatría)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"1. AHA. Part 9: Adult Advanced Life Support: 2025 AHA Guidelines for CPR and ECC. Circulation. 2025.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"2. AHA. Part 11: Post-Cardiac Arrest Care: 2025 AHA Guidelines for CPR and ECC. Circulation. 2025.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"215","text":"3. Perman SM et al. 2023 AHA Focused Update on Adult ACLS. Circulation. 2024;149(5):e254-e273.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"215","text":"4. Berg KM et al. 2024 ILCOR CoSTR Summary. Circulation. 2024.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"215","text":"5. Cheskes S et al. Defibrillation Strategies for Refractory VF. N Engl J Med. 2022;387:1947-56.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"215","text":"6. Ueno R et al. Impact of frailty on survival after IHCA. J Crit Care. 2024;83:154842.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"215","text":"7. Haar M et al. ICU-CA among very elderly patients. Scand J Trauma Resusc Emerg Med. 2024;32:84.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"215","text":"8. Le Maguet P et al. Prevalence and impact of frailty on mortality in elderly ICU patients. Intensive Care Med. 2014;40:674-82.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"215","text":"9. AHA. Older Adults in the Car